#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to store encrypted mails as unencrypted?"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Symptom:</emphasis> You exchange encrypted mail with a friend, but "
"would like to store it unencrypted, once you have opened the message."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Solution:</emphasis> To store emails that have been decrypted once "
"in unencrypted format henceforth, add this to your <filename>kmail2rc</"
"filename> configuration file, in the [Reader] section:"
